title: "Last Call for Democracy."
description: President Biden focuses on democracy as his closing midterm message, Democrats angst over the party's strategy and look for signs of hope in the early vote, Senator Mark Kelly joins to talk about his must win race in Arizona. And later, Jon and Dan play a round of Two Takes and a Fake.
author: hey@crooked.com (Jon Favreau, Dan Pfeiffer)
